725346f-a.title: Queens: 43rd Street - 20th Road
725346f-a.text:
43rd Street, at the S.E. corner of 20th Road, the Old
Bowery Bay Road, showing a fashionable private home of mid-
nineteenth century construction. Et appears on an 1891
atlas, but ownership is not given.
P. L. Sperr  June 3, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
